#~ "terminal with the current document when possible</link> option is "
#~ "enabled, it will change to the directory of the current document if "
#~ "possible when it is displayed, or when the current document changes."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "De ingebouwde terminal, een kopie van &konsole;, de terminal van &kde;, "
